Bangladesh reached 2 for 57 at lunch on day 3 of their second and final Test against Sri Lanka at Mirpur.Mominul Haque was 31 not out.They are chasing a record 339 to win the game and the series.Sri Lanka who began the day on 200 for 8 were bowled out for 226 this morning.Roshen Silva remained 70 not out. Taijul Islam bagged 4 for 76.